{"tid":665184,"cid":19,"subCid":0,"title":"笑話之原來roommate 係nds","createTime":"2018-05-14T17:11:52.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-15T02:34:20.000Z","uid":161659,"like":0,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"5415f820356a6818066a2aceb3f779aae33308ab","tid":665184,"uid":161659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T17:11:52.000Z","msg":"我有個好笑嘅笑話:<br />\n<br />\n我有個朋友，佢roommate 由sem2開始reg，點知冇翻過嚟一晚訓，連見都冇見過。<br />\n<br />\n到咗就嚟退宿嘅時間，我朋友好有衝勁想知道究竟roommate 係咩人<br />\n<br />\n佢打開佢啲筆記，見到一本學英文嘅生字簿，點知translate 出嚟嘅野勁cam，佢對於牛超級講究，對牛每個部位嘅英文都好熟悉，而且每種食物英文譯出嚟嘅中文都好奇怪，用簡體字寫。<br />\n<br />\n再一樣好笑嘅野係，我朋友再睇佢放喺度食譜，點知點食譜得圖畫，完全唔知本野點樣教煮野食。<br />\n<br />\n由嗰一刻開始，我朋友開始諗：<br />\n究竟呢個人喺邊個星球嚟嘅呢？"},{"pid":"2c3ad0755ed13a1eadecdfee61a841cb11636e25","tid":665184,"uid":67252,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T17:13:11.000Z","msg":"好好笑"},{"pid":"9a682a9a34a316660c55364a66164e5f6abc9051","tid":665184,"uid":96,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T17:14:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>好好笑</blockquote>"},{"pid":"ca5c9013ec8794b0cc7ce2a856258d77bbdcac56","tid":665184,"uid":28228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T17:16:31.000Z","msg":"......."},{"pid":"9503095c0b3adbadea63dd2b6201f2bc902b457f","tid":665184,"uid":144784,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T17:17:26.000Z","msg":"個笑話唔得喎搞搞佢"},{"pid":"3b6283cee076205576dadd585428abf5dced3a44","tid":665184,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T17:18:14.000Z","msg":"哈哈&hellip;"},{"pid":"a50c76c26520539bf0ba453d188fa300b619b500","tid":665184,"uid":996,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b6283cee076205576dadd585428abf5dced3a44","tid":665184,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T17:18:14.000Z","msg":"哈哈&hellip;"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-14T17:19:33.000Z","msg":"好尷尬...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cla